Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.74,0:22:46.80,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}让人羡慕的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.16,0:22:52.76,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}朋友（就是我们）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:55.60,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}小小的好奇心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:58.62,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}将成为巨大契机
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:00.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}看吧（看吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.34,0:23:04.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}突然之间就变近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.52,0:23:07.10,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}烦恼与欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.10,0:23:10.22,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}失落与欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:12.80,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}把大家的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:14.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}更多（更多地）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.34,0:23:17.90,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}显露出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:20.68,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}一起来燃烧青春吧（Go!）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:22.20,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}让我们一起（Go!）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:24.76,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}牵着手向前冲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.76,0:23:27.66,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}就算跌倒也不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:31.02,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}大家再一同重新爬起（一二！）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:35.36,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}最喜欢的这个时光（这个时光）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.98,0:23:36.70,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}不要害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.92,0:23:39.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}大声喊出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:42.84,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}因为无论是明天 还是未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.84,0:23:45.78,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}都想要一直欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.78,0:23:48.16,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}这无可替代的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.16,0:23:51.84,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}希望它永不褪色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.84,0:23:54.36,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}持续到永远！

